//! # Usage
//!
//! ```bash
//! cargo run --example cross_border_payment
//! ```
//!
//! # References
//!
//! - IETF draft‑guorong‑utxo‑dns‑01 – UTXO RR specification
//! - BIS Project Agorá – Atomic settlement specification
//! - PRN Security Framework – Compliance and audit
//! - GLEIF vLEI Standard – Legal entity identity

